history.content:
I'm not completely certain at this point, but I just wanted to flag that for many courses including COMPSCI courses, enrollment restrictions are not yet in the system but will be input this week before enrollments begin on April 18.

They will be the same as they have been in the past. See http://www.eecs.berkeley.edu/Policies/enrollment.shtml plus that undergraduates will need instructor permission to be moved from the waitlist into the class for graduate level cs classes.

**EE enrollment restrictions will be added this week as well.
